    {
      "id": "theta-derivation",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 370,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "Key:  |Ψ₀⟩ = |0⟩⊗ⁿ|ψ⟩\n       |Ψ₁⟩ = H⊗ⁿ|0⟩⊗ⁿ|ψ⟩ = (1/√2ⁿ) Σⱼ |j⟩|ψ⟩\n       |Ψ₂⟩ = (1/√2ⁿ) Σⱼ e²ᵖⁱᶿʲ |j⟩|ψ⟩\n       |Ψ₃⟩ = QFT†|Ψ₂⟩ = |2ⁿθ⟩|ψ⟩  (for exact θ)\n       θ̃ = φ/2ⁿ  where φ is the measurement outcome",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#37474f",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
