      "height": 60,
      "text": "Note: The controlled-U²ᵏ gates are the key to QPE. Each control qubit applies U a different number of times:\nQubit 0 → U¹, Qubit 1 → U², Qubit 2 → U⁴, ..., Qubit n-1 → U^{2ⁿ⁻¹}\nThis encodes the phase θ with n bits of precision.",
